    "Figure 1 illustrates the relationship between the frequency of use and the modified Z-scores for words and phrases with absolute modified Z-scores exceeding 3.5 in 2024.",
    "Red circles represent potentially AI-influenced terms, while grey circles represent common academic phrases (controls).",
    "The x-axis shows the number of total records using the words/phrases on a logarithmic scale, and the y-axis displays the modified Z-score for usage frequency.",
    "academic phrases from 2000 to 2024.",
    "Shaded areas represent 95% confidence intervals."
